79"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="405229529"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="406387741"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="437605903"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="1vuvo1kHmgt9IKXGPcBRfI"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="2W8aepbse0n6BhelZ30rUK"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="2jWEiSTx60NHZ89IJoBJAC"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="2tex5GELzJlOFxlBhIiYQ9"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="4jUuqKRr1fB4c1RvU6syls"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="5CM8R2WwihXJz9evO7Rumo"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="5dnS8PkSkJCxThumOIWREp"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="6MKxKSqaaDeCDEhkULgTNC"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="6naxalmIoLFWR0siv8dnQQ"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="7icr4heHIbV9HRq4jkb1m9"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="181228823"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="Watercooling480"/></metadata></head><body dur="3:30.507"><div begin="21.008" end="3:30.507"><p begin="21.008" end="23.810" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="21.008" end="21.269">I</span> <span begin="21.269" end="21.615">think</span> <span begin="21.615" end="21.943">I</span> <span begin="21.943" end="22.225">did</span> <span begin="22.225" end="22.616">it</span> <span begin="22.616" end="23.810">again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我重蹈覆辙了</span></p><p begin="24.136" end="29.165" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="24.136" end="24.431">I</span> <span begin="24.431" end="24.720">made</span> <span begin="24.720" end="25.055">you</span> <span begin="25.055" end="26.390">believe</span> <span begin="26.659" end="26.965">we&apos;re</span> <span begin="26.965" end="27.290">more</span> <span begin="27.290" end="27.602">than</span> <span begin="27.602" end="27.936">just</span> <span begin="27.936" end="29.165">friends</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我让你以为 我们是超越朋友的关系</span></p><p begin="29.812" end="34.085" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.812" end="30.077">Oh,</span> <span begin="30.077" end="30.779">baby,</span> <span begin="30.779" end="31.078">it</span> <span begin="31.376" end="31.823">might</span> <span begin="32.011" end="32.306">seem</span> <span begin="32.306" end="32.602">like</span> <span begin="32.602" end="32.932">a</span> <span begin="32.932" end="34.085">crush</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">哦宝贝 这也许看起来像爱情</span></p><p begin="34.407" end="39.872" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="34.407" end="34.543">But</span> <span begin="34.543" end="34.824">it</span> <span begin="34.824" end="35.521">doesn&apos;t</span> <span begin="35.521" end="36.565">mean</span> <span begin="36.936" end="37.072">that</span> <span begin="37.072" end="37.342">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="37.342" end="37.992">seri</span><span begin="37.992" end="39.872">ous</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但这并不意味着 我是认真的</span></p><p begin="40.192" end="51.531" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.192" end="40.492">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="40.492" end="40.820">to</span> <span begin="40.820" end="41.746">lose</span> <span begin="41.746" end="42.706">all</span> <span begin="42.706" end="43.345">my</span> <span begin="43.345" end="45.108">senses,</span> <span begin="45.283" end="45.557">that</span> <span begin="45.557" end="45.912">is</span> <span begin="45.912" end="46.507">just</span> <span begin="46.507" end="47.119">so</span> <span begin="47.119" end="48.116">typically</span> <span begin="48.116" end="48.846">me,</span> <span begin="49.310" end="49.628">oh,</span> <span begin="49.628" end="50.284">baby,</span> <span begin="50.284" end="51.531">baby</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为失去所有理智 才是真的我</span></p><p begin="50.941" end="56.659" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="50.941" end="51.582">Oops,</span> <span begin="51.582" end="52.160">I</span> <span begin="52.160" end="52.471">did</span> <span begin="52.471" end="52.826">it</span> <span begin="52.826" end="54.104">again,</span> <span begin="54.405" end="54.718">I</span> <span begin="54.718" end="55.029">played</span> <span begin="55.029" end="55.353">with</span> <span begin="55.353" end="55.648">your</span> <span begin="55.648" end="56.659">heart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我又重蹈覆辙了 玩弄了你的心</span></p><p begin="56.953" end="1:01.042" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="56.953" end="57.276">Got</span> <span begin="57.276" end="57.585">lost</span> <span begin="57.585" end="57.900">in</span> <span begin="57.900" end="58.231">the</span> <span begin="58.231" end="59.158">game,</span> <span begin="59.437" end="59.741">oh,</span> <span begin="59.741" end="1:00.433">baby,</span> <span begin="1:00.433" end="1:01.042">baby</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">却迷失在这游戏里 宝贝</span></p><p begin="1:01.042" end="1:08.168" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:01.042" end="1:01.425">Oops,</span> <span begin="1:01.693" end="1:02.284">you</span> <span begin="1:02.284" end="1:02.566">think</span> <span begin="1:02.566" end="1:02.871">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:02.871" end="1:03.238">in</span> <span begin="1:03.238" end="1:04.211">love,</span> <span begin="1:04.510" end="1:04.657">that</span> <span begin="1:04.657" end="1:04.826">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:04.826" end="1:05.152">sent</span> <span begin="1:05.152" end="1:05.450">from</span> <span begin="1:05.450" end="1:05.775">ab</span><span begin="1:05.775" end="1:07.889">o</span><span begin="1:07.889" end="1:08.168">ve</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你以为我在和你恋爱 以为我从天而降</span></p><p begin="1:08.289" end="1:11.200" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:08.289" end="1:08.610">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:08.610" end="1:08.928">not</span> <span begin="1:09.272" end="1:09.628">that</span> <span begin="1:09.888" end="1:11.200">innocent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我没那么天真</span></p><p begin="1:11.441" end="1:14.206" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:11.441" end="1:11.751">You</span> <span begin="1:11.751" end="1:12.068">see,</span> <span begin="1:12.068" end="1:12.376">my</span> <span begin="1:12.376" end="1:13.054">problem</span> <span begin="1:13.054" end="1:13.348">is</span> <span begin="1:13.348" end="1:14.206">this</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你看 我的问题在于</span></p><p begin="1:14.598" end="1:21.300" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:14.598" end="1:14.894">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:14.894" end="1:15.555">dreaming</span> <span begin="1:15.555" end="1:16.837">away,</span> <span begin="1:17.466" end="1:18.056">wishing</span> <span begin="1:18.056" end="1:18.364">that</span> <span begin="1:18.364" end="1:19.380">heroes,</span> <span begin="1:19.380" end="1:19.598">they</span> <span begin="1:19.598" end="1:20.598">truly</span> <span begin="1:20.598" end="1:21.300">exist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我只是在幻想 希望那些传说的英雄真的存在</span></p><p begin="1:21.566" end="1:24.340" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:21.566" end="1:21.830">I</span> <span begin="1:21.830" end="1:22.415">cry,</span> <span begin="1:22.532" end="1:23.112">watching</span> <span begin="1:23.112" end="1:23.409">the</span> <span begin="1:23.409" end="1:24.340">days</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我以泪洗面的那些日子</span></p><p begin="1:24.736" end="1:30.393" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:24.736" end="1:24.844">Can&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:24.844" end="1:25.035">you</span> <span begin="1:25.035" end="1:25.326">see</span> <span begin="1:25.326" end="1:25.616">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:25.616" end="1:25.968">a</span> <span begin="1:25.968" end="1:27.144">fool</span> <span begin="1:27.430" end="1:27.567">in</span> <span begin="1:27.567" end="1:27.842">so</span> <span begin="1:27.842" end="1:28.508">many</span> <span begin="1:28.508" end="1:30.393">ways?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">难道你看不出来我傻吗 有那么多方式保持理智</span></p><p begin="1:30.672" end="1:39.343" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:30.672" end="1:30.973">But</span> <span begin="1:30.973" end="1:31.354">to</span> <span begin="1:31.354" end="1:32.232">lose</span> <span begin="1:32.232" end="1:33.235">all</span> <span begin="1:33.235" end="1:33.819">my</span> <span begin="1:33.819" end="1:35.540">senses,</span> <span begin="1:35.784" end="1:36.055">that</span> <span begin="1:36.055" end="1:36.377">is</span> <span begin="1:36.377" end="1:36.982">just</span> <span begin="1:36.982" end="1:37.604">so</span> <span begin="1:37.604" end="1:38.574">typically</span> <span begin="1:38.574" end="1:39.343">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可是我还是失去理智了 但是这才是真的我</span></p><p begin="1:39.605" end="1:41.166" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:39.605" end="1:39.943">Oh</span> <span begin="1:39.943" end="1:40.419">baby,</span> <span begin="1:40.419" end="1:41.166">oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">宝贝</span></p><p begin="1:41.438" end="1:47.107" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:41.438" end="1:42.070">Oops,</span> <span begin="1:42.070" end="1:42.695">I</span> <span begin="1:42.695" end="1:42.965">did</span> <span begin="1:42.965" end="1:43.275">it</span> <span begin="1:43.275" end="1:44.533">again,</span> <span begin="1:44.922" end="1:45.164">I</span> <span begin="1:45.164" end="1:45.495">played</span> <span begin="1:45.495" end="1:45.827">with</span> <span begin="1:45.827" end="1:46.126">your</span> <span begin="1:46.126" end="1:47.107">heart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我又重蹈覆辙了 玩弄了你的心</span></p><p begin="1:47.429" end="1:51.577" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:47.429" end="1:47.742">Got</span> <span begin="1:47.742" end="1:48.010">lost</span> <span begin="1:48.010" end="1:48.327">in</span> <span begin="1:48.327" end="1:48.689">the</span> <span begin="1:48.689" end="1:49.618">game,</span> <span begin="1:49.975" end="1:50.251">oh,</span> <span begin="1:50.251" end="1:50.865">baby,</span> <span begin="1:50.865" end="1:51.577">baby</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">却迷失在这游戏里 哦宝贝</span></p><p begin="1:51.555" end="1:58.559" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:51.555" end="1:52.152">Oops,</span> <span begin="1:52.152" end="1:52.776">you</span> <span begin="1:52.776" end="1:53.090">think</span> <span begin="1:53.090" end="1:53.400">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:53.400" end="1:53.684">in</span> <span begin="1:53.684" end="1:54.766">love,</span> <span begin="1:55.013" end="1:55.179">that</span> <span begin="1:55.179" end="1:55.329">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:55.329" end="1:55.613">sent</span> <span begin="1:55.613" end="1:55.927">from</span> <span begin="1:55.927" end="1:56.266">ab</span><span begin="1:56.266" end="1:58.329">o</span><span begin="1:58.329" end="1:58.559">ve</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你以为我在和你恋爱 以为我从天而降</span></p><p begin="1:58.769" end="2:01.630" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:58.769" end="1:59.103">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:59.103" end="1:59.512">not</span> <span begin="1:59.729" end="2:00.114">that</span> <span begin="2:00.384" end="2:01.630">innocent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我还没那么天真</span></p><p begin="2:12.220" end="2:13.586" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:12.220" end="2:12.976">All</span> <span begin="2:12.976" end="2:13.586">aboard</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">全体上船</span></p><p begin="2:14.046" end="2:15.590" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:14.046" end="2:14.464">Britney,</span> <span begin="2:14.992" end="2:15.224">before</span> <span begin="2:15.224" end="2:15.341">you</span> <span begin="2:15.341" end="2:15.590">go</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">布兰妮 在你离开前</span></p><p begin="2:15.689" end="2:16.907" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:15.689" end="2:15.838">There&apos;s</span> <span begin="2:15.838" end="2:16.115">something</span> <span begin="2:16.115" end="2:16.211">I</span> <span begin="2:16.211" end="2:16.373">want</span> <span begin="2:16.373" end="2:16.466">you</span> <span begin="2:16.466" end="2:16.550">to</span> <span begin="2:16.550" end="2:16.907">have</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有样东西我想交给你</span></p><p begin="2:17.319" end="2:18.622" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:17.319" end="2:17.647">Oh,</span> <span begin="2:17.647" end="2:17.743">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="2:17.743" end="2:18.622">beautiful</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">哦 太美了</span></p><p begin="2:19.191" end="2:20.718" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:19.191" end="2:19.375">But</span> <span begin="2:19.375" end="2:19.539">wait</span> <span begin="2:19.539" end="2:19.631">a</span> <span begin="2:19.631" end="2:19.871">minute,</span> <span begin="2:20.059" end="2:20.242">isn&apos;t</span> <span begin="2:20.242" end="2:20.718">this?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但是等等 这不是...？</span></p><p begin="2:20.957" end="2:21.780" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:20.957" end="2:21.237">Yeah,</span> <span begin="2:21.237" end="2:21.474">yes,</span> <span begin="2:21.474" end="2:21.573">it</span> <span begin="2:21.573" end="2:21.780">is</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是的 就是那个</span></p><p begin="2:22.515" end="2:25.505" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:22.515" end="2:22.626">But</span> <span begin="2:22.626" end="2:22.789">I</span> <span begin="2:22.789" end="2:22.989">thought</span> <span begin="2:22.989" end="2:23.170">the</span> <span begin="2:23.170" end="2:23.333">old</span> <span begin="2:23.333" end="2:23.681">lady</span> <span begin="2:23.681" end="2:23.822">dropped</span> <span begin="2:23.822" end="2:24.061">it</span> <span begin="2:24.061" end="2:24.330">into</span> <span begin="2:24.330" end="2:24.413">